Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.93,0:00:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫普特利麦奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是GN ARMS  拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始强袭用运输器的对接程序
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与运输器的相对速度OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道  激光  锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN ARMS与强袭用运输器对接完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  相当不错的战果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  洛克恩的情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万幸的是身体上的伤并不严重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是右眼就受创了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在集中治疗室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫雷诺医生  伤口要多久才能恢复？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最少也要三周
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你也知道  一旦进了治疗舱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没治好之前不能出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此期间我们先回船坞把Gundam的整备…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  别随便下决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人不知道什么时候会来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用治疗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  以你的伤根本不能进行精确射击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小瞧我和哈罗的组合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  如果我躺着的话有个家伙会很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么要强  那家伙也很脆弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.19,0:01:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为我过于依赖吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而让他负了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次  我们联合国军将开发能与Gundam对抗的新型MS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:27.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}联合  美国  伊利诺伊基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将此新型机编为特别部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始对Gundam进行扫荡作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战名为Fallen Angels
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于公开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得简直就像是自己造出来的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag的状况呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见  正在全力突击作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最怕等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}人革联  俄罗斯南部  军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  所有GN Drive的压缩空间在临界值上稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-X  启动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在重新开始对Gundam进行扫荡作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-X部队  全体出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会让你们逃掉了…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的整备状况如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue的损伤还有办法处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  驾驶舱的损坏严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁坏成这样  无从修起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得回船坞换一些单元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活动的Gundam只有三台…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么Fallen Angels啊  开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是坠落的天使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  菲露特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是那种年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一直这样多久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像平时那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了作为Meister的资格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能和吠陀直接连接的话  我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吠陀的直接连接…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  Virtue的系统变更出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新系统传送时出错是因为连接中的特瑞亚自身引起了障碍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这种事对于人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不适合当Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是不能连接而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当变得跟我们一样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀被什么人掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吠陀的话  这个计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了根除战争才坐上Gundam战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  实现计划的可能性已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多  做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身边不是就有个做示范的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会按自己的想法乱搞一气的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  我回房间休息去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐也说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败是很正常的啊  因为是人类嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真温柔啊  不管是对谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罐头我都吃腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想吃甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要逃到什么时候啊  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子也剩得不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望将我们和机体一起返回宇宙的事能准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐意效劳…本想这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微晚了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:07:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国军的部队已经朝你们那里出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克尔  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动Throne  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  发现Gundam了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点E8590
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机  迎击队形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克尔  妮娜  Drive的粒子发生率在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩30%吗  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对不起大哥  但我可不会节省的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密集队形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam正在邻国的领空交战？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国的扫荡作战开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是刹那的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快被干掉啊  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为人多就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么笨拙的攻击怎么可能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵的实力  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我们还是Gundam啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用追了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的藏身所已经被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drive的活动界限迟早会到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 6  Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入最终作业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trinity的极限快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  最后的余兴节目  让我期待一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国军终于对Trinity开始攻击了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了击败Gundam  世界在统一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我们是为了被毁灭而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是伊奥利亚·修亨伯格的计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根除战争的机体应该是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Trinity把战火扩大  联合国军也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Gundam要做的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  联合国军对Trinity的攻击也是纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要进行武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经很疲劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道电梯也不能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前受到敌人攻击也是因为Exia和Dynames被敌人跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being不允许沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能没办法再回宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是一个人也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想确认Gundam到底是为什么存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的就老实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭用运输器有冲出大气层的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便也能做GN Arms的性能试验
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在分散战力的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务计划哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不确定因素太多了  可能没什么用处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  强袭用运输器搭载完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive与运输器的对接确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射准备  全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  能得到答案就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭用运输器  拉塞  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去的话  你也可以去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心刹那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:32.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}AEU  高轨道平台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入大气层的机体？所属呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明  但是突入前观测组发现了GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being是想去帮留在地上的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的Drei被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经拜托王留美做上宇宙的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能信任她么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU的Enact
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光通信？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说没有攻击意图？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  在Throne待机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  到处与世界为敌的就是你们吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见  是个佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞助商要我来给你们帮点什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军不是就一架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你来的？  拉古那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那？  啊  你是说拉古那·哈贝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈克哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快逃  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美丽的兄妹之爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点坐上机体如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本打不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥  迈克哥被…  迈克哥被！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会替他报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会？Zwei没有迈克尔的生物识别的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料被改写了吗！？用了吠陀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不习惯的话不方便操作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要知道了武装  之后总有办法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？  为什么对我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是活祭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深表同情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:15:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变这个世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心的去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…我们是为成为Meister而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  而活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子真是漂亮的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来捣乱啊  克鲁吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·沙谢斯！？  为什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会坐上Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7  Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全掌握吠陀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了看到世界的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有苏醒的保证就进入冷冻休眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  很可惜你无法看到世界的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所追求的统一的世界也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为其抑制力的Celestial Being也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都将由我来继承
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界的是我——亚历桑德罗·柯纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本兹  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里出现怀有恶意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说很可惜  世界并没有成为我所追求的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊奥利亚·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统陷阱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类现在还很愚蠢好战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在走向让世界毁灭的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊来啊！怎么啦？Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的人居然坐上Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要你小子的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我还是相信人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想将力量托付给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好准确的射击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  Gundam这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还真是了不得的兵器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得进行战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的Gundam就是为此而存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一来就了结你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？在哪里！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？那种动作是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的背后！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia…  变红了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有GN Drive的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否是我的意识的继承者我并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我想把我最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive的全部能力托付给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈祷你们为了获得真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了根除战争而继续奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是以你们的意识…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同Gundam一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道是什么把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM…系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:17.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}同じ笑顔してた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:24.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}そんな僕らも幾年も重ねすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:28.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}すれ違う景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}受け入れられずにもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:46.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:47.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:53.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:57.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:02.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:07.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:12.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:18.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}忘れちゃいけないからYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:23.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:30.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この広い大地の仲間たちのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:17.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}曾有着相同的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:24.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就是那样的我们也已过了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:28.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那交错的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}无法接受并急躁着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}舍弃了无用的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:46.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}给予这世界以温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:47.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我要说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:53.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即便显示出勇气　即便逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:57.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一个人亦是无法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:02.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}若是那天的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:07.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}依然存留在心灵深处的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:12.58,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如同生命的延续...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:18.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}由于不可忘记　Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:23.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}所以不要离去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:30.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}还要留在这广阔大地同伴们的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界和人的意识改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  反对的意识在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「把世界停住」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不绝的恸哭驻留在漆黑的天空


